increase damage by 50% -Note- 50% of this goes to the lesser damage bounce dagger
increase damage reduction by 8% -Note- 50% of this goes to the lesser damage bounce dagger
increase duration by 0.5
reduce mana cost by 50
reduce cooldown by 3

add a new modifier Poison Dagger
after striking the enemy,they will get poison dealing 11 plus 18% of agility in pure damage per 0.5 second and disabling regeneration
for 3, also increase the damage they take by riki spell by 15% and if their die under the effect of the poison, they will spread it
to other target for 50% increase damage and lasting 2 more second and can also spread again and those will spread, also making it spread
to infinity but those that spread from the Second poison that spread will only have 0.5 duration increase.

SPELL W Blink Stab
jump behind the enemy stunning them and dealing damage, after the stun the target will become silence, riki will also Attack the target
as well Behind them dealing Increase damage with BackStab, the buff duration of the Bonus BackStab damage will last 2.5 seconds.

quick note for the silence and stun scaling, having 100 agility and having 1 level will increase the duration by 10% of agility total of
0.10 seconds bonus, if the scaling for the stun or silence is 50% from 100 agility it will increase it by 0.50 seconds

