add a new modifier Deep Strike
every 5 attacks behind the target will do 200% of Riki attack damage and Agility in Pure damage to them and Riki will lifesteal for 30%
of that damage dealt as well, he also gain 1% damage reduction every time he does his 5 attack, at 5% damage reduction riki will gain
10 agility and 65 movespeed, at 10% damage reduction, Riki will reduce his base attack time by 0.15 and increasing his attack range by
75, max stack of 12% damage reduction, he will lose 2 stacks if he get stun or root, he also become immune to Slows effects.


ULTMATE R Dagger Dance - Physical
Riki Create A Arema of Dagger around him, dealing damage every seconds and each hit done on enemys will reduce their armor and their
magical damage output, Riki will also gain increase Health regeneration and Agility while he Stand in his Dagger Dance. If he exit is
Dagger Dance it will cancel it, Riki also become Perfect Invis, enemys cannot see him or target him and while he is in Dagger Dance
he cannot do normal attacks but cast his spell at will and have them cost 30% less mana and have 40% coldown reduction, the debuff will
refresh on hit of Dagger Dance.

